保时捷使命 X https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/Barry Ritholtz Sun, 18 Jun 2023 15:00:17 +0000 CarsWeekend https://ritholtz.com/?p=314837 <p>保时捷 Mission X 是电动汽车不断战胜内燃机汽车的最新一步。从特斯拉到廉价的入门级比亚迪，再到超级跑车，这是一场改变游戏规则的转变，就像迪伦第一次戴上 Stratocaster 并尽情驰骋时一样。 Mission X 是一款超轻量级超级跑车，取代了 918 Spyder。它是…</p><p><a class="button" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/">阅读更多<i class="icon ion-arrow-right-c"></i></a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/06/porsche-mission-x/">保时捷 Mission X</a>后的照片首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a>上。</p> ; <p><a href="https://www.porsche.com/usa/mission-x/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">保时捷 Mission X</a>是电动汽车不断战胜内燃机汽车的最新一步。从特斯拉到廉价的入门级<a href="https://www.byd.com/us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">比亚迪，</a>再到超级跑车，这是一场改变游戏规则的转变，就像迪伦第一次戴上<a href="https://news.wttw.com/2018/11/20/bob-dylan-s-legendary-electric-guitar-display-chicago" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stratocaster</a>并尽情驰骋时一样。</p><p> Mission X 是一款超轻量级超级跑车，取代了 918 Spyder。它的质量高度集中在驾驶员后面（而不是在乘客舱下方），这使得它不仅速度快而且敏捷。其 1:1 的功率/重量比使其成为有史以来最快的量产车之一，0-60 英里/小时加速时间不到 2 秒。保时捷声称它将成为纽博格林著名的北环赛道上最快的道路合法车辆。该 <a href="https://www.stuttcars.com/the-porsche-mission-x-in-depth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">纪录 6 分 35.18 秒</a>，目前由梅赛德斯-AMG One 保持，本质上是街头合法的一级方程式赛车。</p><p>一些更令人惊讶的细节：</p><blockquote><p> – 功率：~1,480 HP（估计）<br /> – 不寻常的比例：14.8 英尺长，但只有 3.9 英尺高；<br /> – 空气动力阻力优于 911 GT3 RS<br /> – 主动空气动力装置提供超过 1000 磅的下压力；<br /> – 900 V 架构（充电时间约为 Taycan Turbo S 的一半）；<br /> – 驾驶员仪表、中控台和乘客的多个屏幕。<br /> – 剪刀开门</p></blockquote><p>价格尚未公布，但预计限量生产成本将达到 7 位数，并于 2026 年左右交付。</p><p>之前的保时捷超级跑车也同样受到限制：保时捷 959（1986 年至 1993 年生产 300 辆）、Carrera GT（ <a href="https://www.porsche.com/stories/mobility/the-legend-of-the-porsche-carrera-gt-a-classic-sports-car-inspired-by-le-mans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1270 辆</a>）和保时捷 918 插电式混合动力车（ <a href="https://www.porsche.com/stories/innovation/how-much-is-a-porsche-918-spyder" target="_blank" rel="noopener">918 辆</a>）都是小批量生产。</p><p>如果保时捷制造了超过 1000 辆这样的怪物，那将是一个令人惊讶的事情。</p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314838" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-250x141.jpeg 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1536x864.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314840" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="406" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3.jpeg 1440w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-1024x577.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-768x433.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-250x141.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-314843" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="405" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6.jpeg 1035w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/6-768x432.jpeg 768w, htt